dct_description_sm: 4 bar scales on map, given in "The Germanian Miles," "The French Miles," "The Italian Miles," and "Furlongs."
Decorative border and cartouche, ships, sea monsters.
From Speed's A prospect of the most famous parts of the world, London: George Humble, 1627, 1631.
